Body:
Posted in SWAT Channel for Guidance: Saqib Sharif: AIC Applied Permissions Error

posted in SWAT Teams: Product Discussions, PM Q&A, Feedback / NEA Core on Thursday, 7 November 2024 11:35 am

Â

Steps to Reproduce Updated: 1. Search a user in AIC and click it.
2. On the right pane, click on permissions

Next Steps Updated: Bug is resolved as per Bug Fix list and after confirming from the dev team in SWAT. Customer will update and let us know. However, they dont know the exact date for starting the upgrade process. This ticket will be closed as per confirmation of the customer

What We've Learned Updated: The customer is currently using EOS and EOL version 11.0.0.231 of StealthAudit. When they try to view "permissions" against a user searched in AIC, they are observing STATUS 500 code.
